data.name: 0000 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: U-Umm, there's something I've been meaning to ask you about…

data.name: 0001 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hm? What is it, Mikuru?

data.name: 0002 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: It's about Nagato…

data.name: 0003 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What about Yuki?

data.name: 0004 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Weell, she's still a literature club member… right?

data.name: 0005 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you talking about, Mikuru? She's a member of the SOS Brigade.

data.name: 0006 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I-I know that but… That clubroom is also technically still the literature clubroom too.

data.name: 0007 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Well in a way I guess. But in reality, it's the SOS Brigade room. There's no doubt about it.

data.name: 0008 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: In the first place the literature club was a ghost club where Yuki was the only member.

data.name: 0009 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Gh-ghost club?

data.name: 0010 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yeah—it's a term I made up just now. You can't have club activities with just one person.

data.name: 0011 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Y-yeah. That's true…

data.name: 0012 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That's why I'm gonna make the most of Yuki!

data.name: 0013 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: And on top of that, Yuki is a really valuable asset! She's wasted on the literature club!

data.name: 0014 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Don't you agree—Kyon's little sister?

data.name: 0016 (271.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Yup! Agreed agreed!

data.name: 0017 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Ah-haha…

data.name: 0018 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That's why Yuki is a precious member of our group.

data.name: 0019 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: And that clubroom is a precious place for us.

data.name: 0020 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We should call it the secret base, or head- quarters maybe. Some kind of cooler name.

data.name: 0021 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Well, setting that side for now—why would the thing about Yuki bother you?

data.name: 0022 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Eh? U-um well… you see…

data.name: 0023 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I was just thinking, w-won't the student council people get angry at us?

data.name: 0024 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Oh, just that.

data.name: 0025 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You're such a worrywort. It'll be fine—I won't let them interfere with us.

data.name: 0026 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If it comes to it, war might outbreak between the student council and SOS Brigade!

data.name: 0028 (271.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Outbreaking war—!

data.name: 0029 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Th-that's not what I meant…

data.name: 0030 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: In any case, the current student council doesn't even have that kind of vitality.

data.name: 0031 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I doubt they're even doing their job properly.

data.name: 0032 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If there were more worthy opponents for them, they'd burn up.

data.name: 0033 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: #P06…For me, peace is the most important thing—

data.name: 0034 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What did you say?

data.name: 0035 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: N-no, it's nothing—

data.name: 0036 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I see. Then question time is over.

data.name: 0037 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Mm…

data.name: 0038 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We better hurry—Kyon and the others might be slacking off.

data.name: 0039 (271.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Let's go, little sister.

data.name: 0040 (271.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Yep—

data.name: 0041 (271.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I-I wonder if I bought us some time…
